data.description: $26000 PRICE REDUCTION. MOTIVATED SELLER. MAKE AN OFFER! Welcome to Kings Gate, the desirable 55+ gated golf course community in the heart of Port Charlotte. This 3 bed, 1721 square foot home has an open and airy feeling with high ceilings. NEW ROOF 2023 is just one of the pluses. The gourmet kitchen has new vinyl plank flooring, granite counters and stainless appliances with lots of storage. It's perfect for entertaining. The 29' lanai has impact resistant, UV coated windows to make it feel like part of the house. A 400 sf. ft. concrete patio lets you also enjoy your outdoor space. The master ensuite bath has a garden bath, dual sinks and a large Roman shower. The Kings Gate community has options to keep you busy no matter your interests. Thee is an Olympic-size pool and spa, tennis and pickleball courts, fitness center and way more. There is also a 18-hole golf course. The onsite Lions Den restaurant and bar is convenient, or you can go by golf cart to the shopping center next door for shopping and restaurants. The location is near beaches, and other sites in Florida. Don't wait to see this beautiful home. SELLER HAS AN FHA MORTGAGE THAT MAY BE ASSUMABLE UNDER 4% IF BUYER IS QUALIFIES.
